{"tid":1256006,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"一首屬於香港嘅歌","createTime":"2019-06-24T18:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:44:21.000Z","uid":227929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0230a28fa5012c9cf799ae20f61bc274e414a4","tid":1256006,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:43:55.000Z","msg":"《高地教堂》<br />\n詞：Hans J&uuml;rgensmeyer<br />\n<br />\n偉哉香江　我城我等家邦<br />\n傲覽碧海　彪炳戰績輝煌<br />\n仁義禮智　隨伴乘風破浪<br />\n垂範東方　履途挽手逕創<br />\n<br />\n念城邦　立憲遵治道<br />\n歐亞古禮　共冶一爐<br />\n效龍獅　尚智尊道義<br />\n矢勇矢德致志<br />\n<br />\n美哉香江　似洋紫荊茂盛<br />\n耀眼光彩　彰高貴顯尊榮<br />\n苗裔遍世　凝聚同心唱詠<br />\n樂禮鏗鏘　四夷也當謁敬<br />\n<br />\n自由港　未怕海浩瀚<br />\n自強不朽　是我海岸<br />\n太平山　做我等助佑<br />\n敦我克己奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n勇武香港　眾民處變不驚<br />\n盡每分光　光顯社稷威名<br />\n無懼戰鬥　無懼捨生獻命<br />\n榮耀蒼天　至仁至尊至聖<br />\n<br />\nHans Meyer冀藉《高地教堂》一曲，推動香港族群意識。<br />\n<br />\n純音樂 (推薦版本) :<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Yj_3scEyVoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYj_3scEyVoI&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443p6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=ae05e7cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Yj_3scEyVoI</a><br />\n<br />\n純音樂 (中文歌詞) :<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W25Rv3OCr2M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW25Rv3OCr2M&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443p6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=2f0a399d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W25Rv3OCr2M</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東話配音版本 :<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2kdCjFHDKbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2kdCjFHDKbQ&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443p6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=f8ae9c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2kdCjFHDKbQ</a><br />\n(暫時香港淨係得一首廣東話配音，佢唱得唔好聽唔好打我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"81aafcadfaeec9d6923e7b8bc4c0e9b6c9b8bf6f","tid":1256006,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /